This collection of 25 Elvis songs was created to highlight Retro-Audio's 
achievement in remastering selections from Elvis' catalog with such 
crispness and clarity that it astonishes many who listen. 
 
For any fans of Elvis, or any Audiophile looking to add the best-sounding 
Early Rock 'n Roll to their collection (like me), this is a must-have.

Often remastered from Analog Master Tapes, Retro-Audio explains the 
process: "There's tube equipment involved...a tape recorder with partly 
self-built external headamps with tubes which I fine-tuned extremely to 
my preferences. Finally it's digitized with a tube Analog-Digital 
converter. There's absolutely no computer adjustings."

This warm, clean, and expertly mixed analog experience 
is what Elvis fans have been waiting for!

THIS IS A FAN COMPILATION.
